@startuml
!theme plain
hide empty description

[*] --> Composing
Composing --> Composing : Seed / invoke_llm
Composing --> Parsing : LLMResponded / parse_response
Composing --> Failed : BudgetExceeded
Parsing --> Dispatching : ToolCall / $tool
Parsing --> Validating : Completion / validate
Dispatching --> Composing : ToolDone / invoke_llm
